# =============================================================================
# GETTING YOUR CREDENTIALS - STEP BY STEP
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. CREATE IBM CLOUD ACCOUNT:
#    - Go to https://cloud.ibm.com/
#    - Sign up for free account (no credit card required for lite tier)
#
# 2. CREATE WATSONX PROJECT:
#    - Go to IBM Watsonx: https://dataplatform.cloud.ibm.com/wx
#    - Create new project
#    - Note down the PROJECT ID from project settings
#
# 3. GET API KEY:
#    - Go to IBM Cloud console
#    - Navigate: Manage > Access (IAM) > API keys
#    - Click "Create an IBM Cloud API key"
#    - Give it a name like "Learning Emotion Radar"
#    - Copy the API key (you won't see it again!)
#
# 4. SETUP THIS FILE:
#    - Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
#    - Edit .env and replace the placeholder values
#    - Never commit .env to git!
#
# 5. VERIFY SETUP:
#    - Run: python emotion_detector.py
#    - Should see: "âœ… Emotion detector initialized successfully!"
